    • Constructor Detail

      • CsvResultsExporter

        public CsvResultsExporter(PrintStream printStream)
        Construct a new exporter whose output will go to the specified stream.

        The exporter will not close the stream when it is done, or even when its PrintWriterExporter.close() method is invoked. Thus this constructor can be safely used on System.out and similar streams that one usually does not want to close.

        Parameters:
        printStream -
